of your boat, then you're gonna have this

00:20:14.169 --> 00:20:17.150
problem where you don't have any satellites
in view.

00:20:17.150 --> 00:20:20.879
If it's just an aesthetic thing, you're just
really trying to mimic that style, because

00:20:20.879 --> 00:20:24.779
that's what you're used to and you think that
your users will sort of appreciate that.

00:20:24.779 --> 00:20:26.029
That's definitely a choice.

00:20:26.029 --> 00:20:28.299
But I kind of agree with Trevor here, I think.

00:20:28.299 --> 00:20:31.070
You can do that without making it look like
an old Atari game.

00:20:31.070 --> 00:20:32.359
So you've got the same sort of layout.

00:20:32.359 --> 00:20:33.659
The same sort of graphics.

00:20:33.659 --> 00:20:38.080
